2.32 тОХGTK - GTK Interface
=========================

GTK (Gimp ToolKit) is a rather powerful library for creating graphical
user interfaces (GUIs).  тОХGTK makes a subset of the almost 10000
functions in the different GTK libraries available to GNU APL programs.
With тОХGTK a GNU APL program can, for example, replace the somewhat crude
тОХ or тНЮ input methods of standard APL with a more intuitive GUI.

   The details of using тОХGTK would go far beyond the scope of this info
manual and has therefore been put into a separate document.  See:
HOWTOs/Quad-GTK.html.


