2.39.1 Preconditions
--------------------

libpcre2 is NOT shipped with GNU APL but must be installed before the
GNU APL ./configure script is executed.  The ./configure script tries to
locate libpcre2 and enables тОХRE if the library (and its header files)
are found.

   If ./configure does not find libpcre2, then тОХRE will raise a SYNTAX
ERROR when тОХRE is used in an APL program.


