2.45 Conditionals
=================

WARNING: GNU APL conditionals are experimental.  Use them with care and
avoid them, wherever possible, in favor of portability.  Neither the ISO
APL standard, nor IBM APL2 provide conditionals.

* Menu:

* Design considerations.::
