the rather frequent B was chosen to avoid name conflicts between the
right value argument of SHOW_NC and the right value argument the
operators under test (like OPER1 or OPER2).  Then:

           тНЭ Test 2a: binding of the left operand (literal LO)
           тНЭ
           11 22 33 OPER1 1 2 3
     A       : Unused Name
     LO      : Value  11 22 33
     OPER1   : Operator
     B       : Value  1 2 3

           тНЭ Test 2b: binding of the left operand (parser LO)
           тНЭ
           (UU VV WW)тЖР11 22 33
           UU VV WW OPER1 1 2 3
     A       : Unused Name
     LO      : Value  11 22 33
     OPER1   : Operator
